{"tid":1613342,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧斯爾2015神預言：基拿比是我合作過的最佳攻中","createTime":"2019-10-02T13:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T03:48:53.000Z","uid":165817,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8e14065d264654c11876d543079a36953c150f7a","tid":1613342,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:52:22.000Z","msg":"奧斯爾四年前接受阿仙奴官網訪問，選出佢合作過嘅最佳十一人，當時只有兩個阿仙奴隊友入選，除咗魔術師卡叔，就係得基拿比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n四年前個個都笑佢同基拿比，佢唯有話因為基拿比坐喺佢面前，但事實證明佢眼光好撚準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡斯拿斯<br />\n拿姆 拉莫斯 保定 馬些路<br />\n卡蘇拿 阿朗素 基拿比<br />\n迪馬利亞 賓施馬 基斯坦奴<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qw8U76ayxXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQw8U76ayxXc&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHXxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=3129921e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qw8U76ayxXc</a>"},{"pid":"1b02d307ae784199b910d67de392c162940a7757","tid":1613342,"uid":234509,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:57:31.000Z","msg":"四年後<br />\n佢本人變左笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ba068d063e906e1ceaf94494ed674c7a0e748f","tid":1613342,"uid":165817,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1b02d307ae784199b910d67de392c162940a7757","tid":1613342,"uid":234509,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:57:31.000Z","msg":"四年後<br />\n佢本人變左笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"個笑話係艾馬利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e9aa3a198778012b0d776e03fb8fefd9b70c1c","tid":1613342,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:01:36.000